# Proje Yapısı ve Giriş Noktaları

- Frontend (Vite + React 19 + TS)

  - Giriş: [frontend/src/main.tsx](mdc:frontend/src/main.tsx) → [frontend/src/App.tsx](mdc:frontend/src/App.tsx)
  - Router: [frontend/src/App.tsx](mdc:frontend/src/App.tsx)
  - Layoutlar: [frontend/src/layouts](mdc:frontend/src/layouts)
  - Rotalar/Guard: [frontend/src/routes](mdc:frontend/src/routes)
  - Context: [frontend/src/context](mdc:frontend/src/context)
  - Servisler: [frontend/src/services](mdc:frontend/src/services)
  - Ortak Tipler: [frontend/src/types](mdc:frontend/src/types)
  - Altyapı (ENV/HTTP/Query): [frontend/src/lib](mdc:frontend/src/lib)

- Backend (NestJS 10 + TS)
  - Giriş: [backend/src/main.ts](mdc:backend/src/main.ts)
  - Uygulama Modülü: [backend/src/app.module.ts](mdc:backend/src/app.module.ts)
  - Modüller: [backend/src/auth](mdc:backend/src/auth), [backend/src/students](mdc:backend/src/students), [backend/src/lessons](mdc:backend/src/lessons)

# Çalıştırma

- Backend: `cd backend && npm i && npm run start:dev`
- Frontend: `.env.local` → `VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000`, ardından `cd frontend && npm run dev`
